Usage:
  rails generate zen:admin ModelName [field:type field:type]

Description:
    Generates an Admin CRUD controller with Inertia/React pages.

    This generates:
        - Admin controller with CRUD actions
        - React pages (Index, Show, New, Edit) using Ant Design Pro
        - Routes for the resource

Example:
    rails generate zen:admin Article title:string body:text status:integer

    This will create:
        - app/controllers/admin/articles_controller.rb
        - app/frontend/pages/admin/articles/Index.tsx
        - app/frontend/pages/admin/articles/Show.tsx
        - app/frontend/pages/admin/articles/New.tsx
        - app/frontend/pages/admin/articles/Edit.tsx
        - Adds routes to config/routes.rb
